headline: Warner Bros. Gains Streaming Subscribers on Foreign Push
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Warner Bros. Discovery Inc., the parent of the Max streaming service, gained more subscribers than expected in the third quarter, suggesting its online business is picking up.
